<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.1">
<l>tāmukakkun taṅkaiyiṟ caṅkamē pōlāvō</l>
<l>yāmukakku meṅkaiyiṟ caṅkamu mēntiḻaiyīr</l>
<l>tīmukattu nākaṇaimēṟ cērun tiruvaraṅkar</l>
<l>āmukattai nōkkārā lammaṉē yammaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O women bearing ornaments!</l>
<l>Will the conch-shell [bracelets] on our wrists that we delight in</l>
<l rend="indent">compare with the conch in His hand that He delights in?</l>
<l>Ah! The Lord of Srirangam—who joins the bed that is the snake with fiery faces—</l>
<l>will not look at [my] face, alas! Oh dear, oh dear!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
